Â 
The companyâ€™s mission is to leverage the decentralized blockchain structure to create the firstÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
Decentralized Streaming Network (DSN) whereby video viewers are incentivized to shareÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
redundant memory and bandwidth resources to address todayâ€™s video streaming challenges.Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
Using the Ethereum EVM â€œWorld Computerâ€ metaphor, the DSN can be viewed as the â€‹â€œâ€‹WorldÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
Cacheâ€‹â€â€‹ â€‹formed by the memory and bandwidth resources contributed by viewers.Â 
Â 
Specifically, viewers around the globe can contribute their computers as â€‹â€œâ€‹caching nodesâ€‹â€Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
whereby they form a video delivery infrastructure that is responsible for delivering any givenÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
video stream to viewers anywhere around the world. The DSN can effectively address theÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
technical challenges discussed in the previous section. First, viewersâ€™ computers areÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
geographically much closer to each other than to the CDN POPs. This reduces packetÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
round-trip time and improves the stream delivery quality, and thus addresses the â€œlast-mileâ€Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
delivery issue. Second, with sufficient amount of caching nodes, most viewers will receive theÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
stream from caching nodes, this will help streaming sites reduce their CDN bandwidth cost.Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
Third, caching nodes also reduce round-trip time making foveated streaming technologyÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
practical.Â 
Â 
To encourage viewers to contribute their memory and bandwidth resources, we introduce â€‹theÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
Theta protocol as an incentive mechanism. The caching nodes can mine new tokens as theyÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
relay video streams to other viewers. Not only does Theta tokens motivate viewers to join theÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
network as caching nodes, but it also greatly â€‹improves the streaming market efficiency byÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 

8Â 



streamlining the video delivery processâ€‹. We will discuss more details later in the paper, but withinÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
the Theta network, advertisers can directly target viewers at a lower cost, viewers earn ThetaÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
tokens for their attention and engagement with video streams, and influencers earn ThetaÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
token as gifts directly from viewers.Â 
Â 
The full launch of the Theta protocol in phase II introduces a â€‹new blockchain and a â€‹native tokenÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
structure where:Â 
Â 

â— Advertisers spend tokens to support influencers, streaming sites and viewersÂ 
â— Caching nodes mine new tokens for caching and relaying video streamsÂ 
â— Viewers optionally earn tokens from advertisers as engagement rewardsÂ 

