Â 
The Theta protocol builds upon the following novel concepts:Â 
Â 
Â 

â— Reputation Dependent Mining: â€‹In the Theta protocol, â€‹the caching nodes play the role ofÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
miners in the blockchainâ€‹. Similar to other blockchains, the caching nodes validateÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
transactions and attempt to add new transaction blocks to the blockchain based onÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
Proof-of-Work. However, in our protocol, the block reward is not a constant. â€‹TheÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
miners with higher â€‹reputation score â€‹(intuitively this means that they serve viewers moreÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
effectively) will have a higher block rewardâ€‹. To obtain more mining rewards, miners notÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
only spend computation power to mine blocks, but also relay video streams toÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
downstream viewers to maintain and increase their reputation scores. In other words,Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
they are essentially â€œfunctional minersâ€.Â 

Â 
â— Global Reputation Consensus: We propose a scalable mechanism for the ThetaÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 

network to reach the global consensus on the reputation scores for each caching node,Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
and thus the global consensus on the amount of mining reward for each block.Â 

Â 
â— Proof-of-Engagement: We devised a novel Proof-of-Engagement (PoE) scheme toÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 

ensure that viewers legitimately consume the video streamsâ€‹. Viewers can earn tokens asÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
rewards from advertisers in exchange for their attention to video streams and byÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
providing Proof-of-Engagement. PoE not only brings benefits to viewers, but also toÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
advertisers as it provides them with a reliable and verifiable engagementÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
measurement of the delivered video streams.Â 

