Token Flow Among StakeholdersÂ 
Â 
Caching nodes play the roles of miners in the blockchain. As they validate the transactions andÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
add new blocks to the chain, tokens â€‹Tokenâ€‹POW are awarded to them. In the Theta blockchain,Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
