higher block reward when they mine a new block. This motivates the caching nodes to relayÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
video streams to more viewers and more efficiently. We will dive into more detail later in theÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
paper.Â 
