Note that in practice, a user might watch a video stream while running the caching nodeÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
software on his or her computer. In such a case, â€‹the userâ€™s computer is both a viewer and aÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
caching nodeâ€‹. This allows the viewers to earn mining rewards as a caching node, and thenÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
optionally gift to influencers. This is represented by the dashed red rectangular box in Figure 5.Â 
Â 
