return they reward â€‹Tokenâ€‹I to the ingest nodes. And optionally the ingest nodes tip â€‹Tokenâ€‹F toÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
influencers.Â Â 
Â 
For the ad-supported streams, advertisers typically allocate a marketing budget, â€‹Tokenâ€‹Aâ€‹, asÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
shown in Figure 5. A majority of this budget, â€‹Tokenâ€‹Sâ€‹, is spent to sponsor influencers orÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
streaming sites. The remaining portion, â€‹Tokenâ€‹Vâ€‹, is optionally used as an engagement rewardÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
for viewers of the stream, namely:Â 
