Function â€‹fâ€‹(â€‹Tâ€‹totalâ€‹) is a monotonically increasing function which maps â€‹Tâ€‹total to a real number in theÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
