reputation score and the hash value.Â 

Â 
â— All the Theta token transactions are valid. The validity conditions are the same asÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 

Bitcoin.Â 
Â 

â— The validator miner verifies the reputation score â€‹r is computed correctly based on theÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
