the block body. They can be stored either by the caching miner node that mined the new block,Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
or on decentralized storage systems such as IPFS/SWARM.Â 
