constant. Each set also has a header containing two numbers, the set index â€‹iâ€‹, and â€‹Tâ€‹iâ€‹, the sumÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
of the serving time for each certificate (calculated using Equation (6)) in the set.Â 
Â 
The root of the merkle tree is stored on-chain in the header of the newly mined block toÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
prevent potential tampering of the service certificates. In addition, the accumulated serviceÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â 
time of each set of certificates â€‹Tâ€‹1â€‹, â€‹Tâ€‹2â€‹, â€¦, â€‹Tâ€‹nâ€‹ are also added to the block header.Â 

